16. Lambda Limits
	- Execution
		-> Memory allocation: 128 MB - 10 GB
		-> Max execution time: 15 min (900 seconds)
		-> Env variables: 4KB
		-> Disk capacity (/tmp): 512MB to 10GB
		-> Concurrency executions: 1000 (can be increased)
	- Deployment
		-> Lambda function deployment size .zip: 50MB
		-> Lambda function uncompressed deployment (code + dependencies): 250MB	
